Class InputEntry

java.lang.Object
  plugins.ccuration.index.InputEntry
All Implemented Interfaces:
ContentCurationConstants
public class InputEntry
extends java.lang.Object
implements ContentCurationConstants

This container stores all the tpe (TermPageEntry) related to one document and the identity who publishes it. The constructor extract the terms from title, document's name, and keywords and generate one tpe for each.
